        "body": "## Summary\n\nImprove Simplified Chinese (`zh-Hans`) localization quality for visible CodexBar UI.\n\nThis PR focuses on user-visible zh-Hans polish in menu/card/dashboard areas:\n\n- menu actions and labels\n- usage/pace labels\n- storage/cost/credits and chart helper text\n- cleanup panel visible labels\n- MiniMax visible usage detail labels in menu UI\n\nIt fixes mixed Chinese/English labels in visible UI paths by routing labels through localization, adding missing keys, and polishing Simplified Chinese terminology.\n\n## Scope\n\n- No new language added\n- `zh-Hant` untouched\n- No provider data semantics changes\n- Product/provider/model names remain unchanged\n- Model usage keeps `token`; API/auth contexts use `令牌`\n\n## Files\n\n21 files changed, centered on:\n\n- `Sources/CodexBar/Resources/en.lproj/Localizable.strings`\n- `Sources/CodexBar/Resources/zh-Hans.lproj/Localizable.strings`\n- visible UI localization call sites\n- formatting helpers used by visible menu/card/chart UI\n\n## Validation\n\n- `plutil -lint Sources/CodexBar/Resources/en.lproj/Localizable.strings` ✅\n- `plutil -lint Sources/CodexBar/Resources/zh-Hans.lproj/Localizable.strings` ✅\n- `./Scripts/lint.sh lint` ✅\n- `swift build --target CodexBarCore` ✅\n- `swift test --filter Localization` ✅\n- `git diff --check` ✅\n\n## Local proof\n\nTested with a freshly built local app using `appLanguage = zh-Hans`.\n\nThe app process path was confirmed as the local PR worktree build:\n`/Users/yuxinqiao/Developer/CodexBar-zh-hans-visible-ui/CodexBar.app`\n\nand not `/Applications/CodexBar.app`.\n\nLocal proof screenshots were captured under `artifacts/` for manual review. They contain local account/session/usage details, so they were not committed or uploaded unredacted.\n",
